{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyVersion"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ApplicationRef","text":"ApplicationRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14ApplicationRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyVersion"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::version"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}],"name":"Note"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"onNotifyVersion(flags:handler:)","extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO19ApplicationProtocolPAAE15onNotifyVersion5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0B3RefV_AG09ParamSpecM0VtctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO11ApplicationC","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyVersion","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"text":"ApplicationRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14ApplicationRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/onNotifyVersion(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/application\/onnotifyversion(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations"]]},"abstract":